## Remarks  
<span data-ttu-id="0ca32-208">如果当前 <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> 表示泛型方法定义，则：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-208">If the current <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> represents a generic method definition, then:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="0ca32-209">`IsGenericMethodDefinition` 返回 `true`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-209">`IsGenericMethodDefinition` returns `true`.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="0ca32-210">对于该 <xref:System.Type> 方法返回的数组中的每个对象 <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.GetGenericArguments> ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-210">For each <xref:System.Type> object in the array returned by the <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.GetGenericArguments> method:</span></span>

      - <span data-ttu-id="0ca32-211"><xref:System.Type.IsGenericParameter?displayProperty=nameWithType> 属性返回 `true`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-211">The <xref:System.Type.IsGenericParameter?displayProperty=nameWithType> property returns `true`.</span></span>

      - <span data-ttu-id="0ca32-212"><xref:System.Type.DeclaringMethod?displayProperty=nameWithType>返回当前的 <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-212">The <xref:System.Type.DeclaringMethod?displayProperty=nameWithType> returns the current <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo>.</span></span>

      - <span data-ttu-id="0ca32-213"><xref:System.Type.GenericParameterPosition?displayProperty=nameWithType>属性与 <xref:System.Type> 对象在数组中的位置相同。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-213">The <xref:System.Type.GenericParameterPosition?displayProperty=nameWithType> property is the same as the position of the <xref:System.Type> object in the array.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="0ca32-214">使用 `IsGenericMethodDefinition` 属性可确定是否已将类型参数分配给泛型方法的类型参数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-214">Use the `IsGenericMethodDefinition` property to determine whether type arguments have been assigned to the type parameters of a generic method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0ca32-215">如果已分配类型参数， `IsGenericMethodDefinition` 即使某些类型参数是 <xref:System.Type> 表示封闭类型的类型参数的对象，属性也会返回 false。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-215">If type arguments have been assigned, the `IsGenericMethodDefinition` property returns false even if some of the type arguments are <xref:System.Type> objects that represent type parameters of enclosing types.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0ca32-216">例如，请考虑以下 C \# 、Visual Basic 和 c + + 代码：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-216">For example, consider the following C\#, Visual Basic, and C++ code:</span></span>

    ```cs
    class C
    {
        T N<T,U>(T t, U u) {...}
        public V M<V>(V v)
        {
            return N<V,int>(v, 42);
        }
    }
    ```

    ```vb
    Class C
        Public Function N(Of T,U)(ByVal ta As T, ByVal ua As U) As T
            ...
        End Function
        Public Function M(Of V)(ByVal va As V ) As V
            Return N(Of V, Integer)(va, 42)
        End Function
    End Class
    ```

    ```cpp
    ref class C
    {
    private:
        generic <typename T, typename U> T N(T t, U u) {...}
    public:
        generic <typename V> V M(V v)
        {
            return N<V, int>(v, 42);
        }
    };
    ```

<span data-ttu-id="0ca32-217">M 的方法体包含对方法 N 的调用，该方法指定 M 的类型参数和类型 <xref:System.Int32> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-217">The method body of M contains a call to method N, specifying the type parameter of M and the type <xref:System.Int32>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0ca32-218">`IsGenericMethodDefinition`对于方法，属性返回 false `N<V,int>` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-218">The `IsGenericMethodDefinition` property returns false for method `N<V,int>`.</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="0ca32-219">尽管在 `N<V,int>` 通过 c 类反射时未遇到开放构造方法，但必须使用生成该方法才能将 <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.MakeGenericMethod%2A> C 作为动态类发出。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-219">Although the open constructed method `N<V,int>` is not encountered when reflecting over class C, it must be generated using <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.MakeGenericMethod%2A> in order to emit C as a dynamic class.</span></span>


<span data-ttu-id="0ca32-220">如果泛型方法定义包含声明类型的泛型参数，则会有特定于每个构造类型的泛型方法定义。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-220">If a generic method definition includes generic parameters of the declaring type, there will be a generic method definition specific to each constructed type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0ca32-221">例如，请考虑以下 C \# 和 Visual Basic 代码：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-221">For example, consider the following C\# and Visual Basic code:</span></span>

    ```csharp
    class B<U,V> {}
    class C<T> { public B<T,S> M<S>() {...}}
    ```

    ```vb
    Class B(Of U, V)
    End Class
    Class C(Of T)
        Public Function M(Of S)() As B(Of T, S)
            ...
        End Function
    End Class
    ```

    ```cpp
    generic <typename U, typename V> ref class B {};
    generic <typename T> ref class C
    {
    public:
        generic <typename S> B<T,S>^ M() {...};
    };
    ```

<span data-ttu-id="0ca32-222">在构造类型中 `C<int>` (`C(Of Integer)` Visual Basic) 中，泛型方法 M 返回 `B<int, S>` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-222">In the constructed type `C<int>` (`C(Of Integer)` in Visual Basic), the generic method M returns `B<int, S>`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0ca32-223">在 open 类型中 `C<T>` ，M 返回 `B<T, S>` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-223">In the open type `C<T>`, M returns `B<T, S>`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0ca32-224">在这两种情况下， `IsGenericMethodDefinition` 属性将返回 `true` <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> 表示 M 的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-224">In both cases, the `IsGenericMethodDefinition` property returns `true` for the <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> that represents M.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="0ca32-225">有关特定于泛型方法的术语的固定条件列表，请参见 <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.IsGenericMethod> 属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-225">For a list of the invariant conditions for terms specific to generic methods, see the <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.IsGenericMethod> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0ca32-226">有关泛型反射中使用的其他术语的固定条件列表，请参见 <xref:System.Type.IsGenericType> 属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-226">For a list of the invariant conditions for other terms used in generic reflection, see the <xref:System.Type.IsGenericType> property.</span></span>

