## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0ca32-234">使用 <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.MakeGenericMethod%2A> 方法，可以编写将特定类型分配给泛型方法定义的类型参数的代码，从而创建 <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> 表示特定构造方法的对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-234">The <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.MakeGenericMethod%2A> method allows you to write code that assigns specific types to the type parameters of a generic method definition, thus creating a <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> object that represents a particular constructed method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0ca32-235">如果 <xref:System.Reflection.MethodBase.ContainsGenericParameters%2A> 此对象的属性 <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> 返回 `true` ，则可以使用它来调用方法或创建委托以调用方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-235">If the <xref:System.Reflection.MethodBase.ContainsGenericParameters%2A> property of this <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> object returns `true`, you can use it to invoke the method or to create a delegate to invoke the method.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0ca32-236">用方法构造的方法 <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.MakeGenericMethod%2A> 可以是开放的，也就是说，它们的某些类型参数可以是封闭泛型类型的类型参数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-236">Methods constructed with the <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.MakeGenericMethod%2A> method can be open, that is, some of their type arguments can be type parameters of enclosing generic types.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0ca32-237">生成动态程序集时，可以使用此类开放式构造方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-237">You might use such open constructed methods when you generate dynamic assemblies.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0ca32-238">例如，请考虑以下 c #、Visual Basic 和 c + + 代码。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ca32-238">For example, consider the following C#, Visual Basic, and C++ code.</span></span>  
  
```  
class C  
{  
    T N<T,U>(T t, U u) {...}  
    public V M<V>(V v)  
    {  
        return N<V,int>(v, 42);  
    }  
}  
  
Class C  
    Public Function N(Of T,U)(ByVal ta As T, ByVal ua As U) As T  
        ...  
    End Function  
    Public Function M(Of V)(ByVal va As V ) As V  
        Return N(Of V, Integer)(va, 42)  
    End Function  
End Class  
  
ref class C  
{  
private:  
    generic <typename T, typename U> T N(T t, U u) {...}  
